	</div>
	<div class="grid-article-bd">
		<h1 class="smart-dotdotdot">苹果新专利，把磁性接口都叠在一起？</h1>
	</div>
	<div class="grid-article-ft  clearfix">
		<span class="smart-date" data-originDate="2016-03-30 16:45:43 +0800"></span>
		<div class="ribbon">
		</div>
